The '''''Radiance''''' was a [[Passenger liner/Legends|passenger liner]] that ferried beings down to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] surface after they arrived in-[[Star system/Legends|system]]. When [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Bria Tharen]] visited the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] in [[10 BBY/Legends|10 BBY]], they were shuttled planetside aboard this [[Starship/Legends|ship]].

